<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_124_r1l22">Den von Rotemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_124_r1l23"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als eẅr erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> . mıt etlıchen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> . von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l24">geredt vnd gebetten hat / 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ wır <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> . <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> volkmeır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l25">vnd noch eınen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>ratgeſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / auf den drıtten pfıngſtag ſchıerıſt gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l26">winſheim ʒuleıhen / Dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das alſo an vns bracht / Vnd alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l27"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır das vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / aber tun . <expan>W<ex>er</ex>e</expan> aber ob darein ıcht fıel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l28">/ daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> tag nıht fürſıch gıeng . / das lıeſʒt vns ʒeıtlıch beuor <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l29">Denn als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehſt auch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / von <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l30"><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> den Jr leıpdınggült pflıchtıg ſeyt ʒu <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l31">dıe <expan>beklag<ex>en</ex></expan> ſıch noch daʒ Jn kein <expan>auſʒrıchtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> von ewch geſchehe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l32"><expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> aber dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l33">auſʒ <expan>ʒurıcht<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd vnklaghaft ʒu <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> nach <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> brıef lawt </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_125" id="61v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l1">vnd ſag / vnd vns <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> eyntreg niht ʒu ʒıehet . den <expan>worte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l2"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> deſt <expan>gern<ex>er</ex></expan> tun <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> was <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> lıeb vnd dıenſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l3">ıſt / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
