</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_124" id="61r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Rotemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>Fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ewr erber
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> mit etlichen
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> geredt und gebetten hat,
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Volkmeir und noch einen
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">auf den dritten pfingstag
                                schierist</q>28.05.1420</note>
</app> gen Winsheim zuleihen, die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das also an
                        uns bracht, und also <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir das umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> aber tun; <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> aber,
                        ob darein icht fiel, daz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> tag niht fürsich
                        gieng, das lieszt uns zeitlich bevor <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn
                        als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst auch
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, den ir leipdinggült pflichtig seyt zu
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, die <expan>beklag<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        sich noch, daz in kein <expan>auszrichtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> von ewch
                        geschehe. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> aber die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on
                                <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehen</expan>
<expan>auszzuricht<ex>en</ex></expan> und unklaghaft zu
                                <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> nach <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        brief lawt<pb facs="#facs_125" id="61v"/> und sag und uns
                            <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> eyntreg niht zu ziehet, den
                                <expan>worte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> dest <expan>gern<ex>er</ex></expan> tun
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> was <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> lieb und dienst ist.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>.</ab>
</div>
